Incrediable. Epic. And amazingly made. Mass Effect 2 is an excellent-well written story taking place right after the first Mass Effect.  This game gave me the feeling that I am leading a team of professional soldiers, scientist, and assassins on mission so dangerous that chances of survivale are slim.  This game among the Mass Effect trilogy shall not be forgotten, And I hope to see the Mass Effect Universe expand further in the future.  10/10

